{"tid":1393254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線一半人都缺氣密護目鏡!!! 買野之前入黎睇!!  [200多位前線實測數據]","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:26:06.000Z","uid":105976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3995ce0ab9a5ad1f16df1e9e6f05889a7928c746","tid":1393254,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"(暫時結果同200位果時係相約  所以唔做更新住)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家自留一套防具  日常/重要時候帶/戴出街 讓前線免於恐懼   <br />\n令防具變日常  前線就唔會被針對到</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">結論:<br />\n<br />\n1.前線最缺係氣密護目鏡  而係香港係極難買 可以買既都買到斷貨 (網購)<br />\n所以希望大家幫幫手 繼續搵下邊度可以買到/訂到/網購到 氣密&amp;otg(可以戴眼鏡)&amp;防撞護目鏡<br />\n(下方SPREADSHEET內有講解)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 前線救火隊完全缺安全滅火裝備   希望有長型焊接手套</span> (下方SPREADSHEET內有講解)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">3. 下次豬嘴&amp;豬嘴配件一定供過於求 唔該大家幫手買多d 氣密護目鏡/ 救火裝備 / 護具(身體/手)</span></strong></span><br />\n(下方SPREADSHEET內有講解)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全防具超詳細介紹&amp;購買連結 強烈建議睇  用PC開</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5ybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=6872615f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有人幫手搵以下既氣密護目鏡 人在外國既巴絲應該會易買d</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n可戴眼鏡(OTG), 氣密 (non-vented) 護目鏡:  一定要NON VENTED<br />\n1. Bolle - Coverall Sealed Autoclave OTG goggles NON-vented<br />\n2. JACKSON SAFETY 16677 OTG goggles NON-vented<br />\n3. SELLSTORM Odyssey II OTG NON-vented fire goggles<br />\n4 SELLSTORM 812 non-vented OTG goggles<br />\n5. Uvex Strategy OTG non-vented goggles<br />\n<br />\n氣密 (non-vented) 護目鏡: (不能戴眼鏡)<br />\n6. Bolle Cobra TPR NON-vented goggles<br />\n7. Bolle Superblast Non-vented goggles<br />\n8. 3M GoggleGear(TM) non-vented goggles<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n200位前線實測數據<br />\nA.<br />\n第1位 雙罐豬嘴+60926 100%完美OR少少味 (可能因為佢少配件 最少接合位 就唔會漏氣入黎) (728表現因資料太少未能確認)<br />\n<br />\n第2位 雙罐豬嘴+ 600x罐+502+ 2000系列棉 (92%完美OR少少味)(728表現也一致)<br />\n第3位係 雙罐豬嘴+ 直接用P100 濾棉 (84%完美OR少少味) (728表現因資料太少未能確認)<br />\n第4位係 單罐3200+3311K (80%完美or少少味, 完防比例得17%) (728表現也一致)<br />\n第5位係 雙罐豬嘴+600x罐 (有42%話效果好) (728表現因資料太少未能確認)"},{"pid":"efc104a8984773dee4155599d34e1414aaf1070d","tid":1393254,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351b01e7979379fe53eae1c5a2fa25cac66f6765","tid":1393254,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"帶泳鏡唔得？"},{"pid":"1da0b1134ef96c7f07ef59faf0d80dde91066fe1","tid":1393254,"uid":110507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6978d3cfb5b535f54f9516d6e1d215691b04cc2","tid":1393254,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351b01e7979379fe53eae1c5a2fa25cac66f6765","tid":1393254,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"帶泳鏡唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"得"},{"pid":"451874bccc81066610f5881106d25122bdd181ba","tid":1393254,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"33698e3ee9d96c7fc407cb70354d8fb4f301a188","tid":1393254,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351b01e7979379fe53eae1c5a2fa25cac66f6765","tid":1393254,"uid":5120